    <h1 class="cs-h2 cs-h2--display-wide">Turning a Desktop Portal into a Mobile Operating Layer</h1>
    <p class="cs-hero-sub cs-hero-sub--wide">Defined BabyQuip&rsquo;s first provider app around weekly planning, reservation context, and time-sensitive work &mdash; a focused mobile V1 built by reorganizing capabilities the platform already owned.</p>

