        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="cs-stat-grid-value">4 <span class="cs-stat-annotation--xs">of 5</span></div>
          <div class="cs-stat-grid-caption">Said conversations moved off-platform almost always</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="cs-stat-grid-value">0 <span class="cs-stat-annotation--xs">of 5</span></div>
