        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="cs-footnote-block">Internal providers also described monitoring BabyQuip <em>emails</em> rather than the portal inbox &mdash; reinforcing that the platform&rsquo;s communication surfaces were being routed around, not used. Four of five also named switching between tools as a major friction.</p>
